<div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q">How does CRM integration work?</button><div class="faq-a"><p>Automatic synchronisation. An order from your CRM reaches the warehouse &rarr; gets picked &rarr; gets shipped &rarr; status is synced back to your CRM.</p></div></div>
